name: Grade PreK 4-Pack Activity Books
short_description: Smart! The workbook series from edgeucational publishing is designed to give kids the "edge" they need in school. Their lessons cover math, reading, problem solving and writing for pre-kindergarten through fifth grade. The workbooks make learning fun by introducing kids to characters who take them through each activity.
